    <h1>How Do I Set Up TikTok Events API on Shopify Without Code?</h1>
    <div class="quick-answer">
      <div class="qa-label">&#9654; Direct Answer</div>
      <p>Set up a <strong>Shopify order webhook</strong> pointing to Make.com, then configure Make.com to POST a <code style="font-family:var(--mono);background:rgba(255,255,255,.07);padding:2px 6px;border-radius:3px;">CompletePayment</code> event to TikTok's Events API endpoint. <strong>No code required</strong> — uses Make.com's visual builder and TikTok's free API. Takes <strong>6 minutes</strong>. Recovers 20–40% of TikTok conversions lost to iOS and ad blockers, achieving EMQ scores of 6–8.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="https://stackarchitect.xyz/tiktok-events-api-shopify" class="btn pulse" target="_self" >View Full TikTok CAPI Guide &rarr;</a>
      <a href="https://stackarchitect.xyz/" class="btn-outline btn-sm">See All Free Tools &rarr;</a>
    </div>
